\frac{1}{(1-x)^{k+1}}
F(x)=\sum_{i=0}^{\infty}\binom{k}{i}x^{i}\sum_{p=0}^{\infty}\binom{k+p}{p}x^{p}.
F(x)=\frac{1}{(1-x)^{k+1}}\sum_{i=0}^{\infty}\binom{k}{i}x^{i}=\frac{\left(1+x\right)^{k}}{(1-x)^{k+1}}
